DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/145976/', '[1] "Product Information. Zeposia (ozanimod)." Celgene Corporation, Summit, NJ.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] "Product Information. Zeposia (ozanimod)." Celgene Corporation, Summit, NJ.', 1767369485);
