Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/145999/', '[1] "Product Information. Rinvoq (upadacitinib)." AbbVie US LLC, North Chicago, IL.', 1767369485);
